org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.network.cmacs

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.network.NetworkNode
      • org.hswgt.teachingbox.core.rl.network.cmacs.Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Copyable<NetworkNode>

    public class Tile
extends NetworkNode
    * A Tile with position and dimensions (width in each dimension). 
       1 +---------+++++++++++++++++++++----------+
     +                                        +
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
 0.8 +                                        +
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
 0.6 +                                        +
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
 0.4 +                                        +
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
 0.2 +                                        +
     |                                        |
     |                                        |
     +                                        +
   0 +++++++++++---------+---------++++++++++++
    -2        -1         0         1          2         3         4         5
    Example: 
        // create new Tile with position=0 and width=1.
    Tile tile = new Tile(0,2);
    // get the value at 0.5
    double v = tile.getValue(0.5);
